race.description: Celestial Legend @ Woodside Park C&G Handicap
race.comment: CASH CONVERTER (5) is a consistent type who has placed three of four this time in. Steps out further in journey for the first time in a while but did just miss when last over a similar journey. Overdue and should go close again. WHERE'S POPPY (4) was well off best form last time when ninth at Swan Hill. Allen goes back aboard and he has a good record on the gelding. Capable of sharp improvement. MAGICK MEDIA (10)  is a progressive type who was off the mark two back then turned in a poor run at the latest. Drawn for a good run and worth another chance. HANDY FRIEND (6) is resuming from a lay-off. Fitter for a recent trial at Tatura. Opened last campaign with a win at Wodonga over 1300m. Include.
